name: MOTOROLA C113a
description: MOTOROLA C113a is the model of the first mobile phone I owned when I moved to Canada in 2008. It doesn't work anymore, but I still have this phone as a keepsake of a new chapter in my life, a connection to family and friends. If you find an edition of this NFT in your collection, it means we may have a connection. This connection may grow, and holding onto this edition may provide an answer to that. You may also donate or sell this edition.
